General.Name: Vonex Ltd
General.Description: Vonex Limited provides telecommunications services to business customers in Australia and the United States. The company operates through Retail Telecommunications and Wholesale Telecommunications segments. The Retail Telecommunications segment offers data, internet, billing, and other services, as well as voice services, including IP voice services. The Wholesale Telecommunications segment provides Vonex PBX and call termination services, and NBN and 4G mobile broadband at wholesale rates via a white label model. Vonex Limited is headquartered in Milton, Australia.
